&lt;p&gt;They came out better than expected! Some of the gifs are a bit choppy, and my suspicion is it&amp;rsquo;s related to my shooting speed (the M10 has 2 speeds). Seeing them, I think the one with the old, rusted motorboat looks best &amp;mdash; and has the most potential for telling a story. It will be paired with a handdrawn animation. I have tried a simple one before:&lt;/p&gt;

